stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending : 创建评测任务
    Pending --> Running : 调度执行
    Running --> Calculating : 推理完成
    Calculating --> Success : 报告生成完成
    Success --> [*]
    Running --> Failed : 执行异常
    Calculating --> Failed : 指标计算异常
    Failed --> Pending : 重试
    Failed --> Cancelled : 人工终止
    Cancelled --> [*]
